                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/af52ff0a-a4ea-11e0-b786-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/af52ff0a-a4ea-11e0-b786-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_204e failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;/mnt/lustre/d0.sanity/d204 has raw stripe count &apos;1&apos;, not &apos;0&apos;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
