                            <comment id="17323" author="adilger" created="Wed, 6 Jul 2011 16:37:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is missing functionality on that branch, so not really a regression.  The ORI-241 bug will be fixed during the Orion development.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17293" author="prakash" created="Wed, 6 Jul 2011 11:25:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ahh, ok. Since it only deals with the Orian branch, is it still something I should look into?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17280" author="adilger" created="Wed, 6 Jul 2011 03:07:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This test failure is actually only happening in the orion branch, due to a change in the code that is not yet supporting the raw xattr handling.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A bug has been filed for that project (ORI-241) to track this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
